These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: american, french, german, brazilian
Pet: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. Pet:mouse is on the left of Nationality:german##1
2. Nationality:american is on the left of Pet:goat##1
3. Nationality:brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:horse is on the left or right of Pet:mouse##3
5. Nationality:american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | french | brazilian | german |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Sport: climbing, surfing, snowboarding, water-polo
Nationality: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. Sport:surfing is on the left of Sport:water-polo##1
2. Nationality:french is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:french == Sport:climbing##1
5. Nationality:german is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
6. Nationality:french == Sport:climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | snowboarding | climbing  | surfing  | water-polo |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
House: tower, modern, cape-cod, palace
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. House:palace is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. House:cape-cod is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of House:modern##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. House:modern is on the right of House:cape-cod##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| House          | palace | cape-cod | modern    | tower      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

