4. Pet:snake is on the left of Pet:rat##1
5. Pet:rat is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. Pet:snake is in an even position##4
7. Pet:horse == Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
